Requirements
===========================
1) Mac OS X Lion (or greater)
2) Xcode (xcodebuild will be used to build ogre and cegui + compillers and unix tools to build libogg, libvorbis)
3) Cmake (will be used to build alure, mjin, mj)
4) Doxygen (required to build ogre documentation)
5) Graphviz (required to build ogre documentation)

How to build
===========================
Full cycle build:
./build.sh

Fast build, skips existent dirs:
FASTBUILD=Y ./build.sh